{"tid":12872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"免錢的最貴　醫生接受女病患口交被勒索","createTime":"2016-11-29T23:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T00:21:15.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5274f48fbf0caccd079dfbcad4622c5522168e6","tid":12872,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/073344_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F073344_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=db2fb2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲伯斯一名女病患里德利(Anna Marie Ridley)被指控，在2013年11月幫醫生拉爾(Vipin Lal)進行「口交服務」後，竟勒索對方，法院正審理相關案件。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據《西澳洲人報》報導，醫生拉爾本周一在庭上表示，最初向警方作供時，只透露里德利勒索他1萬澳幣(約新台幣23萬元)，並沒有提及對方曾幫他口交，是因為當時他沒勇氣說出口。拉爾說，里德利是他的長期病人，2013年11月某日她來看病時，突然親吻他臉頰，又緊抱他，然後把他推到牆邊。說時遲、那時快，里德利立刻扒下拉爾的褲子，讓拉爾的下體「舉頭望日光，低頭來口交」，她跪下來為拉爾口交。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n拉爾說，當時他不知所措，不想驚動任何人，也不知要如何向擔任診所接待員的太太解釋。他稱里德利數日後再來看病，並勒索他，要求他給錢，並否認曾撫摸里德利的胸部和私處。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n里德利則反駁，稱拉爾在說謊，說這2年下來始終被拉爾視為攻擊者，她相信法官會相信她是清白善良的。審訊依舊持續中。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"a15bdb4ac487e080e077c639009783af54c5c733","tid":12872,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54475c0d74c3b9f44c8ca9d0d923dae6066c11bf","tid":12872,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇者"},{"pid":"71f258562505d2cdb1787f3a3a16cb388800758f","tid":12872,"uid":10725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"「舉頭望日光，低頭來口交」<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32459770a0443a9cc7894be78992067e6529a16c","tid":12872,"uid":490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「舉頭望日光，低頭來口交」<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間教會"}]}